100004/http://www.sankeibiz.jp/business/news/160806/bsc1608060500005-n2.htm |archivedate=2020-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vgtime.com/topic/8350.jhtml |title=Capcom社长：要是玩家老是死，我得让他们跳过这段 |author=猫村ノ村長 |publisher=[[游戏时光|游戏时光]] |language=zh-cn |deadurl=no |date=2016-08-06 |accessdate=2020-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312100133/https://www.vgtime.com/topic/8350.jhtml |archivedate=2020-03-12 }}</ref>。

