rchive.org/web/20160628152907/http://www.pcgamer.com/resident-evil-7-wont-feature-quick-time-events/ |archivedate=2016-06-28}}</ref>。截至2016年7月，該體驗版已被下載超過200萬次<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vgtime.com/topic/7833.jhtml |title=《生化危机7》DEMO下载量突破200万 官方“解释”假手指用途 |author=政宗 |publisher=[[游戏时光|游戏时光]] |language=zh-cn |deadurl=no |date=2016-07-02 |accessdate=2020-03-06 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200306223435/http://www.vgtime.com/topic/7833.jhtml |archivedate=2020-03-06 }}</ref>。9月15日，發布了新的遊戲預告片及《最初时刻》名為「Twilight Version」的更新<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vgtime.com/topic/9007.jhtml |title=《生化危机7》Demo开始更新，新预告释出 |author=沁雅畅慧 |publisher=[[游戏时光|游戏时光]] |language=zh-cn |deadurl=no |date=2016-09-15 |accessdate=2020-03-06 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200306224614/http://www.vgtime.com/topic/9007.jhtml |archivedate=2020-03-06 }}</ref>，增加了新的房間與物品<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/09/15/resident-evil-7-biohazard-beginning-hour-demo-updated-with-new-areas |title=Resident Evil 7 Biohazard Beginning Hour Demo Updated With New Areas |first=Joe |last=Skrebels |work=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |date=2016-09-15 |accessdate=2020-03-06 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200306224948/https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/09/15/resident-evil-7-biohazard-beginning-hour-demo-updated-with-new-areas |archivedate=2020-03-06 }}</ref>。12月3日，另一個更新「Midnight Version」發布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-12-03-resident-evil-7s-beginning-hour-demo-has-just-been-updated |title=Resident Evil 7's Beginning Hour demo has just been updated |first=Aoife |last=Wilson |work=Eurogamer |publisher=Gamer Network |date=2016-12-03 |accessdate=2020-03-06 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306230130/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-12-03-resident-evil-7s-beginning-hour-demo-has-just-been-updated |archivedate=2020-03-06}}</ref>，《最初时刻》於12月9日登陸[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]，12月19日登陸[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Wind