==评价==
=== 發售前 ===
《生化危機7》的游戏試玩《厨房惊魂》初次公佈就獲得不少好評，逼真的畫面、周遭的聲音以及最後出現環抱主角的血手嚇到不少試玩者<ref>{{cite web|title=PS4 虛擬實境裝置「Project Morpheus」首度在台舉辦體驗會 吉田修平分享設計理念 |url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=117176 |author=Sam |publisher=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |language=zh-tw |date=2015-06-30 |accessdate=2020-03-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304164659/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=117176 |archivedate=2020-03-04}}</ref>。澳洲Kotaku的記者稱這款是他「最令人不安的體驗」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2015/06/the-kitchen-on-project-morpheus-will-devour-your-soul/?_ga=2.129525004.1003619312.1583339600-1834553348.1576517993 |title=The Kitchen On Project Morpheus Will Devour Your Soul |first=Chris |last=Jager |website=[[Kotaku|澳洲Kotaku]] |publisher={{link-en|Univision Communications}} |date=2015-06-22 |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304165254/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2015/06/the-kitchen-on-project-morpheus-will-devour-your-soul/?_ga=2.129525004.1003619312.1583339600-1834553348.1576517993 |archivedate=2020-03-04 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>，[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]也給予同樣評價，並期待完成品的到來<ref name="Digital Spy Review" />。自遊戲發布以來，因其[[第一人稱視角|第一人稱視角]]的設計讓許多玩家不禁比較《[[P.T.|P.T.]]》，卡普空特地聲明表示遊戲早在2014年就已經開始製作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/many-are-calling-resident-evil-7-the-new-silent-hills-but-its-so-much-more-than-that/ |title=Many are calling Resident Evil 7 'the new Silent Hills'... but it's so much more than that |first=Andy |last=Hartup |date=2016-06-14 |accessdate=2016-06-15 |website=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160615114035/http://www.gamesradar.com/many-are-calling-resident-evil-7-the-new-silent-hills-but-its-so-much-more-than-that/ |archivedate=2016-06-15}}</ref>。《生化危機7》回歸系列以往的生存恐怖及注重解謎要素，造成了喜歡動作射擊粉絲的不滿<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ent.163.com/game/17/0121/17/CBAPDPMH00314V8J.html |title=要文斗还是要武斗？《生化危机》面临的二选一 |author=铁士代诺201 |publisher=网易 |language=zh-cn |date=2017-01-21 |accessdate=2020-03-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310064914/https://ent.163.com/game/17/0121/17/CBAPDPMH00314V8J.html |archivedate=2020-03-10}}</ref>。

