ite web |url=https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2017/02/06/resident-evil-7-biohazard-comanda-le-classifiche-italiane-week-4-2017/ |script-title=it:Resident Evil 7 biohazard comanda le classifiche italiane (week 4, 2017) |last=Ullo |first=Edoardo |publisher=IlVideogioco |date=2017-02-06 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |language=it |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229134504/https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2017/02/06/resident-evil-7-biohazard-comanda-le-classifiche-italiane-week-4-2017/ |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2017/02/13/resident-evil-7-biohazard-the-sims-4-guidano-le-classifiche-italiane-week-5-2017/ |script-title=it:Resident Evil 7 biohazard e The Sims 4 guidano le classifiche italiane (Week 5, 2017) |last=Ullo |first=Edoardo |publisher=IlVideogioco |date=2017-02-13 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |language=it |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229134623/https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2017/02/13/resident-evil-7-biohazard-the-sims-4-guidano-le-classifiche-italiane-week-5-2017/ |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://ukie.org.uk/news/2017/02/second-week-no1-%E2%80%98resident-evil-vii-biohazard%E2%80%99 |title=Second week at No1 for ‘Resident Evil VII: Biohazard’ |first=Luke |last=Hebblethwaite |publisher={{Link-en|ukie|Association for UK Interactive Entertainment}} |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2017-02-06 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229131826/https://ukie.org.uk/news/2017/02/second-week-no1-%E2%80%98resident-evil-vii-biohazard%E2%80%99 |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref>。根據官方的統計，截至1月30日，共有8萬7千名玩家嘗試過PlayStation VR遊玩<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-01-30-capcom-says-almost-10-percent-of-resident-evil-7-users-played-in-vr |title=Almost 87,000 Resident Evil 7 users have tried the game in PSVR |first=Matthew |last=Handrahan |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2017-01-30 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229134902/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-01-30-capcom-says-almost-10-percent-of-resident-evil-7-users-played-in-vr |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref>。本作是1月最暢銷的电子游戏，在英國、美國及德國都獲得了銷售冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-02-01-resident-evil-7-tops-uk-january-charts-after-less-than-a-week-on-sale |title=Resident Evil 7 tops UK January charts after less than a week on sale |first=Christopher |last=Dring |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2017-02-01 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229132047/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-02-01-resident-evil-7-tops-uk-january-charts-after-less-than-a-week-on-sale |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/02/16/resident-evil-7-was-the-best-selling-game-of-january-2017 |title=Resident Evil 7 Was the Best-Selling Game of January 2017 |first=Seth G. |last=Macy |website=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2017-02-16 |accessdate=2017-02-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217014353/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/02/16/resident-evil-7-was-the-best-selling-game-of-january-2017 |archivedate=2017-02-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.game.de/marktdaten/top-20-games-pc-konsole-januar-2017/ |script-title=de:Top 20 Games PC & Konsole – Januar 2017 |publisher=game.de |deadurl=no |language=de |date=2017-02-14 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229133119/https://www.game.de/marktdaten/top-20-games-pc-konsole-januar-2017/ |archivedate=2020-02-29 }}</ref>。

在遊戲發售前，卡普空预期本作能在3月底售出400万套<ref name="sales cap">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-7-and-dead-rising-4-sales-projection/1100-6444883/ |title=Resident Evil 7 and Dead Rising 4 Sales Projections Revealed |first=Eddie |last=Makuch |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2016-10-28 |accessdate=2016-11-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103160059/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-7-and-dead-rising-4-sales-projection/1100-6444883/ |deadurl=no |language=en |archivedate=2016-11-03}}</ref>。遊戲發售三天共售出250萬套並在同年2月初順利收回成本<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/news/html/e170127.html |title=RESIDENT EVIL 7 biohazard Ships Over 2.5 Million Worldwide! |publisher=[[卡普空|卡普空]] |date=2017-01-27 |accessdate=2017-05-31 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20170531020953/http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/news/html/e170127.html |archivedate=2017-05-31 }}</ref><ref name="budget">{{cite web|url=http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/data/pdf/explanation/2016/3rd/explanation_2016_3rd_03.pdf |title=Third-Quarter Consolidated Financial Results Conference Call for the Fiscal Year ending March 31, 2017: Q&A Summary |publisher=[[卡普空|卡普空]] |date=2017-02-01 |accessdate=2017-02-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227124202/http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/data/pdf/explanation/2016/3rd/explanation_2016_3rd_03.pdf |archivedate=2017-02-27}}</ref>。2017年4月，卡普空宣布《生化危機7》共售出350万套<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-04-27-resident-evil-7-sales-top-3-5m-worldwide |title=Resident Evil 7 sales top 3.5m worldwide |first=Tom |last=Phillips |work=Eurogamer |publisher=Gamer Network |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2017-04-27 |accessdate=2017-04-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427202542/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-04-27-resident-evil-7-sales-top-3-5m-worldwide |archivedate=2017-04-27}}</ref>，但350万套低於當初的預期，受其影響，卡普空在[[东京股票交易所|东京股票交易所]]的{{link-en|股票价格|Share price}}下跌超过3个百分点<ref name="stock price">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/capcom-shares-fall-after-resident-7-ships-fewer-co/1100-6447397/ |title=Capcom Shares Fall After Resident 7 Ships Fewer Copies Than Past Games |first=Eddie |last=Makuch |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2017-01-30 |accessdate=2017-05-31 |deadurl=no |language=en |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20170531021226/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/capcom-shares-fall-after-resident-7-ships-fewer-co/1100-6447397/ |archivedate=2017-05-31}}</ref>。隔年，卡普空歐洲的營運長斯圖亞特·特納（Stuart Turner）接受訪談表示「（現在公司）寧願做出一款評價9分但賣得不好的遊戲，也不要做一款6分但賣更好的遊戲。」，說明公司和以前相比更加注重遊戲的評價。訪談中也提到《生化危機7》自發售兩年來，一直是[[PlayStation_VR|PlayStation VR]]的熱門遊戲<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-08-03-capcom-taken-aback-by-resident-evil-2-reception |title=Capcom: "We'd prefer a game that got a 9 and sold less, than a 6 but sold more." |first=Christopher |last=Dring |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |deadurl=no |language=en |date=2018-08-06 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229135917/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-08-03-capcom-taken-aback-by-resident-evil-2-reception |archivedate=2020-02-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/35847/capcom-wants-game-get-9-scores-but-sell-less-then-poor-reviews-and-sell-more |title=卡普空：情願叫好不叫座，也不要遊戲評價差大賣 |author=湯包 |publisher=[[4gamers|4gamers]] |deadurl=no |language=zh-tw |date=2018-08-07 |accessdate=2020-02-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200229140049/https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/35847/capcom-wants-game-get-9-scores-but-sell-less-then-poor-reviews-and-sell-more |archivedate=2020-02-29}}</ref>。

同年5月，卡普空在综合各方評價、市场及後續DLC發布等各項因素后，预测本作最终能售出1千万套<ref name="lifetime">{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-7-expected-to-ship-10-million-units-/1100-6450098/ |title=Resident Evil 7 Expected To Ship 10 Million Units, Still Has A Lot Of Work To Do |first=Eddie |last=Makuch |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2017-05-16 |accessdate=2017-05-31 |archivedate=2017-05-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20170531022706/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-7-expected-to-ship-10-million-units-/1100-6450098/ |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>。2021年10月，卡普空宣布本作總銷量突破1千萬套<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=222236|title=系列首次的創舉！《惡靈古堡 7》銷售量突破一千萬套|publisher=巴哈姆特|accessdate=2021-10-10|archive-date=2021-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129075936/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=222236|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為系列作第一部銷量破千萬的作品<ref name="Capcom">{{cite web |url=https://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/news/html/211008.html |script-title=ja:『バイオハザード7　レジデント イービル』が全世界で1,000万本を突破！ |website=[[卡普空|卡普空]] |date=2021-10-08 |accessdate=2021-10-08 |deadurl=no |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008021747/https://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/news/html/211008.html |archivedate=2021-10-08 }}</ref>。

